{"tid":1657874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"‎【冷氣軍師掃盲】98.6%接受到攻擊警察，92.9%接受到扔汽油彈？","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T15:55:51.000Z","uid":39244,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5eb9972818302eceae5ca1e02ae8f680f6d2cd","tid":1657874,"uid":39244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1657658/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1657658/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kenTWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kenTWm.png&h=cd7ccff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條問題係先問所有受訪者，「當大型和平示威都未能令政府回應時，示威者有激烈行動係可以理解」，回答可以理解激烈行動(59.2%)或者一般(13.1%)先會再追問「有沒有什麼行動是難以接受的」<br />\n<br />\n換言之，正確解讀應該係同路人(約佔香港7成人)入面<br />\n1. 44.4%核爆都唔割<br />\n2. 最容易接受到打狗，其次係破壞交通燈<br />\n  (1.6%接受唔到打狗 1.8%接受唔到破壞交通燈)<br />\n3. 最難接受裝修黨鐵(23.8%) 機構商店(14.9%)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"39aae2d380b4612e1fd728d924289ca365cd8ed7","tid":1657874,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"9124a61baaef80263d95291b6a30624c5d374b30","tid":1657874,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:46:03.000Z","msg":"個人認為可以將界線定到80%<br />\n一個行動得到8成人支持就足夠<br />\n對付警察睇黎可以再殘忍暴力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c6084f4215ac5e1e12e7b13146219b24074bca","tid":1657874,"uid":278712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"其實破壞港鐵是最不影響「人命安全」（對什麼立場的人也是），偏偏最多人不能接受，香港人究竟有幾鍾意返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"